 data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/\"><strong>Turner Asphalt<\/strong><\/a> is an elite pavement maintenance company proudly serving the greater Southeast. Our offices are strategically located in multiple cities across the Carolinas, with our corporate headquarters in <a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/locations\/raleigh\/\">Raleigh, North Carolina<\/a>. Turner Asphalt is a licensed and insured contractor with nearly 30 years of experience ready to help you or your business with all your paving problems and needs.<\/p><p>While our offices are located in <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/locations\/north-carolina\/\">North<\/a><\/strong> and <a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/locations\/south-carolina\/\"><strong>South<\/strong> <strong>Carolina<\/strong><\/a>, we happily serve customers throughout the Southeast, including <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/locations\/nashville\/\">Tennessee<\/a><\/strong>, <a href=\"https:\/\/turnerasphalt.com\/locations\/atlanta\/\"><strong>Georgia<\/strong><\/a>, Virginia, and Florida. Turner Asphalt is experienced in dealing with various state and local governments and ensuring our processes and materials comply with their regulations. Laws around road construction, environmental impact, and utilities are different between states, and we pride ourselves on offering a seamless experience regardless of the customer\u2019s state or location.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19877e8 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"19877e8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elem